{"tid":2164704,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黨員最新必讀書籍：《帶頭過緊日子》","createTime":"2020-08-19T10:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T13:04:38.000Z","uid":48040,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"388499a42b95b3537bdeaaa94f16e5f4f0e3a61a","tid":2164704,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"黨員最新必讀書籍《帶頭過緊日子》正式出版。<br />\n<br />\n2019年3月， 中國國務院總理李克強在政府工作報告中指出，「各級政府要過緊日子，想方設法籌集資金。」就在同一天，中共總書記習近平在他所在的內蒙古代表團參加審議時指出， &ldquo;黨和政府帶頭過緊日子，目的是為老百姓過好日子&rdquo;。自此， &ldquo;過緊日子&rdquo;就經常掛在中國領導人咀邊。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">到最近， &ldquo;帶頭過緊日子&rdquo;更編寫成書籍，跟其他黨員必讀刊物看齊，作者亦是編寫黨中央大部分指定讀物的任仲文。</span><br />\n<br />\n新書封面引用了習近平於2019年的講話， &ldquo;用黨和政府的緊日子換百姓的好日子&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/WUL0819A-08192020032338.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2FWUL0819A-08192020032338.html&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=8b58aaac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/WUL0819A-08192020032338.html</a>"},{"pid":"9cac73344418aa0ba1d1f75cc43a2bab38d78fd4","tid":2164704,"uid":306598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"點解你俾人踢爆咗扭曲新聞都可以咁勤力出 post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，換個 account la 五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dOu7FJW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOu7FJW.png&h=1dec54b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，只有33%的民主黨人認為要對中國強硬<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fLswmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fLswmS</a>"},{"pid":"0c0c3aa0e947eddbb99ca924342a8dc765272337","tid":2164704,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"邊度緊？下面？"},{"pid":"e947995324c71c4da00827727c55